@{fg shine}History@{fg text}

19.09.1995      V1.00   First release.

20.09.1995      V1.01   If MultiCX-Icon is not available, defaultvalue
                        for mouseblanker is now 0.

                        Gui now opens, if MultiCX-Icon is not available,
                        but SAVE and TEST - buttons are disabled.

                        Removed some useless spaces in SCREEN 2 page.

                        Fixed bug with cycling pages.

                        If ToolType EXTPREFS does not exist or Gadget
                        EXTPREFS is empty then EXTPREFS tooltype is
                        automatically added to MultiCX icon with :
                        'RUN >NIL <NIL: Path/PrefsProgramName'

                        Some Checkmarks set no tooltype value. Fixed.

                        Will find MultiCX icon if it has another name
                        than MultiCX.info.

21.09.1995      V1.02   Fixed a bug in GetToolTypes.

                        No more forgotten ')' at end of tooltype (hope so).

                        Size limits now up to 1000000.

                        Now finds exact path to MultiCX icon.

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.08.

24.09.1995      V1.03   Now added menu for faster access to pages.

                        Changed Cancel gadget to Quit.

25.09.1995      V1.04   Now supports MultiCX 2.09.

                        Changed design of system page.

                        NM_BARLABEL used instead of simple "----" in
                        Project menu.

                        Code shorted about 1.5 K. to V1.03.

25.09.1995      V1.05   Code shorted again about 8 K to V1.04

26.09.1995      V1.06   Now supports MultiCX 2.10.

27.09.1995      V1.07   Now supports MultiCX 2.11.

                        Added NODISPLAYBEEP to screens #1 page.

                        Added NOBOOTWRITE and IOALERT to disk page.

28.09.1995      V1.08   Added ALERTTIME to system page

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.12.

04.10.1995      V1.09   Internal Version

                        Rewritten complete code for tooltype recognizing.

06.10.1995      V1.10   Now supports MultiCX 2.15

                        If MultiCX is not running, only the TEST option is
                        disabled. Saving prefs to icon is now possible.
                        Choose icon from filerequester. If valid, tooltypes
                        are saved to this icon and program quits.

                        If MultiCX is started while MUI_MCX_PREFS is
                        running, all gadgets are set to actual tooltype
                        values from running MultiCX program and SAVE option
                        will be enabled.

14.10.1995      V1.11   Now supports MultiCX 2.18

                        Window title could be trashed sometimes. Fixed.

                        Now using timer.device for permanent semaphore
                        checking. Updating every second seems to be enough.

                        Reduced code 4.2K to V1.10

18.10.1995      V1.12   Forgotten to disable menuitem TEST, when MultiCX 
                        was not running. Fixed.

                        Added menuitem 'Start MultiCX'. If not running 
                        MultiCX can now be launched via WBStart-Handler.

                        Added tooltype MULTICXPATH.
                        (Should be like 'SYS:WBStartup/MultiCX').
                        If tooltype is disabled, MultiCX can't be launched
                        if it is not running.

                        Added installer script.

                        Added WBStart-Handler to archive.

20.10.1995      V1.13   If you start MUI_MCX_Prefs from CLI you can now use
                        argument for MultiCX path. (Should be like 
                        'MULTICXPATH="SYS:WBStartup/MultiCX"')

22.10.1995      V1.14   Added STARTPRI to Misc menu. This is not a MultiCX
                        tooltype, but may be useful to start MultiCX with
                        a higher oder lower prio than 0.

02.12.1995      V1.15   Checkmark gadgets couldn't be controlled by keys
                        since V1.13 , fixed.

                        Tabcycle didn't work since V1.13. Fixed.

                        Now using new Tabcycling routine.
        
                        Added BubbleHelp for all gadgets.

                        Added new tooltypes SHAPESTICK, S_FIRE, S_RIGHT
                        S_LEFT, S_UP, S_DOWN, OPAQQUAL, WBONLY and SMARTWB.  

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.25.

02.12.1995      V1.16   Added tooltype WBGAUGE.

                        Added ShowWarning. If flag is unset and program quits
                        by saving no warning will be shown next time using
                        program.

                        Added Bubble Help. If flag is unset and program
                        quits by saving, the BubbleHelp is sitched off
                        when using program next time.

                        Inserting a special dummy tooltype for SwazInfo,
                        because SwazInfo can't handle the 96th tooltype
                        correct. If there is no special dummy it will be
                        inserted automatically to your MultiCX.info file.

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.26.

05.12.1995      V1.17   Moved PopUp HotKey to misc page. It's the better
                        place for this.

                        Changed StartPri string object to slider object.

                        Added CLIPUNIT slider to system page.

13.12.1995      V2.00   Completly rewritten. This results in shorter code
                        (aprox. 17k) and less memory usage.

                        New GUI, coz MUI 3.x didn't give us the posibility
                        to have cycle gadgets instead of register pages.

                        From now on it is shareware. Please support the
                        idea of shareware!

                        If you need bubblehelp then activate bubblehelp
                        gadget in misc page. From now on the bubbles are
                        available. Deactivating switches bubblehelp of.

13.12.1995      V2.01   Corrected some bugs in bubblehelp texts.

                        Bubblehelp for Quit gadget was not set. Fixed.

                        Could crash, if muimaster.library version < 11
                        Fixed.

14.12.1995      V2.02   If TD values are not set, they will now be set
                        to default values.

                        If MOIRE values are not set, they will be set
                        to default values.

                        WBGAUGE changed to cycle gadget.

                        Corrected some bugs in bubblehelp texts.

16.12.1995      V2.03   Internal Version.

18.12.1995      V2.04   Now fully localized. Feel free to add different
                        catalogs, but please send them to me first!

                        Fixed several small bugs.

23.12.1995      V2.05   Reduced code 2.5k.

                        Removed optical bug in disk page.

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.36.

25.12.1995      V2.06   Internal Version.

                        Reduced code again 1k.                        

26.12.1995      V2.07   Public release.

27.12.1995      V2.08   Added new tooltypes CLOCK, 12HRS, COMPACT.

                        New german catalog (version 1.01) 

                        If wrong version of the catalog is installed, MCXP
                        will use the default language. Be sure to install
                        newest catalog, when installing MCXP!

                        Now supports MultiCX 2.37.

28.12.1995      V2.09   Fixed a bug with SAVE option. (Program quits, when
                        MCX was disabled and no icon was choosen with the
                        filerequester.)

                        Fixed a bug with QUIT option. (Program couldn't
                        quit, when MCX was disabled and new settings
                        tested before.)

                        Fixed a bug in german catalog. IOALERT and NOCLICK
                        was changed by mistake. New catalog version 1.02.

                        STARTPRI and DONOTWAIT tooltypes will not longer 
                        be written, if tooltypes are not saved to MCX's
                        info file.

                        Code for recognizing tooltypes completely
                        rewritten. The sequence of the tooltypes is
                        no longer mixed by program. Unknown tooltypes
                        are now recognized and will be written back
                        with testing and saving. Special gfx informations
                        ( from NewIcons ) are no longer stripped with
                        testing and saving.

29.12.1995      V2.10   Sorry, but gfx informations was written back a bit
                        wrong. Stupid error! Fixed.

01.01.1996      V2.11   Changed some parts of catalog. New catalog version
                        is 1.04.

                        Changed CLIPUNIT slider to numeric button.

                        Changed WINCYCLE slider to numeric button.

                        Added tooltype IGNORE_CLASS to misc page.
                        Future disappeared.

                        Added tooltypes NOCMDKEY and NOESCKEY to 
                        patch/system page.

01.01.1996      V2.12   Is there no one out there who can
                        stop Martin ? ;-)

                        Added tooltype GURUTIME to patch/system page.

                        Changed ALERTTIME slider to numeric button.

                        Fixed gfx bug in patch/system page.

                        New catalog version 1.05. Minimum catalog
                        version requiered is 1.04. (To be sure that
                        underscores always work, You have to install
                        the actual catalog(s). Otherwise it might
                        be you can act on 2 ore more buttons with 
                        the same key)
                           
13.01.1996      V2.13   Enterascii has changed to cyclegadget due
                        to a change in MCX version 2.41.

                        New catalog version 1.06. Minimum version
                        required is 1.04.

23.01.1996      V2.14   New Tooltype AUTOMOUNT added to patch/misc page.
                        New catalog version is 1.07 and is required!
                       
22.02.1996      V3.00   Most parts are rewritten to make it a bit easier
                        to do changes in a more easy way for me.

                        Two locks were left when using Catalogs. Now fixed.

                        If You use an older version of MultiCX with a newer
                        version of MCXPrefs, new tooltypes which are
                        supported with MCXP are now added to MultiCX's
                        tooltype list. May be not very usefull, but You
                        don't have to add new tooltypes to MultiCX's icon
                        any longer.

                        Many changes done to the catalog. Actual catalog
                        version is 2.00!

                        Added some frame titles now. Looks a bit nicer.

                        Now warning if MultiCX versions are not fully supported
                        by MCXP (older oder newer than supported).

                        Added double space for ExternPrefs string.

                        Info requester no longer shown when running
                        program. The requester is now only available on
                        About in menu. You don't have to click it away
                        everytime You use program.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.45.    

02.03.1996      V3.01   Fixed bug with closing timer device after running.

13.03.1996      V3.02   Fixed a bug with locked pubscreen.

                        Fixed enforcer hits which occured with some
                        tooltypes enclosed in brackets. Thanks Martin!

15.03.1996      V3.03   Now works with the new wbstart.library. If not
                        found MCXP will use WBStart-Handler instead!

                        New catalog version 2.01.

                        Added wbstart.library instead of WBStart-Handler to 
                        the archive.

18.03.1996      V3.04   Added tooltype IGNOREKEY to blanker/blanker page.

                        Added tooltype NOCLOSEWB to screen/patch page.

                        WBStart-Handler again added to l-directory of
                        archive (wbstart.library only works with OS3.x or
                        better. The installer script itselfs installs either
                        the library or the handler depending on your OS
                        version!)

18.03.1996      V3.05   Fixed a graphical bug in blanker/blanker page.

                        Minimum catalog version reqired is 2.02

04.04.1996      V3.10   Rewritten from buggy BlitzBasic to AmigaE.

                        Code is approx. 14K shorter now.

                        Fixed bug with NOSIMPLE tooltype. Wasn't
                        recognized correctly.

                        If running under OS version 37 or 38 no longer
                        deadloops when wbstart.library was missing.

                        If using WBStart-Handler (OS version < 39) the
                        handler will now be started first, if
                        WBStart-Handler Port isn't found.

                        When tested a configuration and switching off
                        MultiCX afterwards, the program now asks you if
                        you want to go on or force quit, if you didn't
                        choose a icon to store the tooltypes to. 

                        Reading and writing tooltypes should now be much
                        faster.

                        If a tooltypes has a defaultvalue and you don't
                        change this value, the tooltype is now put in
                        brackets. (E.g. ClipUnit and GuruTime have a 
                        default value.

                        New catalog version v3.10 required.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.47.
 
                        !!! ----------- Attention Attention ----------- !!!

                        * This was a big rewrite and my first step in using
                        * AmigaE. If you find any errors ore bugs please
                        * send me a bug report as fast as you can. 

11.04.1996      V3.11   Error messages are not longer displayed as text by
                        opening a cli window. Now using easyrequester!

26.04.1996      V3.12   Fixed to run as SingelTask program again.

                        Some new translation to catalog file. Version is
                        3.12. You may still use 3.10.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.49.

                        Added german doc file.

30.04.1996      V3.13   SingleTask option crashed, when tired to running 
                        twice. Fixed.

                        Added new own tooltype to run in any language.
                        (LANGUAGE=<language>). The settings of preferences
                        will be ignored. (E.G. If language installed is
                        english You can force german texts by using
                        LANGUAGE=deutsch)
                        [Wished by Nils Goers]

                        Fixed wrong version string in catalog file.     
                        [Reported by Nils Goers]

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.50.

22.05.1996      V3.14   The ESC / Closegadget didn't set the tooltypes
                        to the old values after testing. Fixed now.

                        Screenmode and device requester changed to pop-
                        up requesters.

                        NoBootWrite didn't recognize it's key. Fixed.

                        New catalog version 3.14.

23.05.1996      V3.15   PopCliStack had some problems with it's default
                        value. Fixed.

28.05.1996      V3.16   The backgroundcolor for groups was newer set. Fixed.

                        Added Settings/MUI to menubar

                        New catalog version 3.16 needed.

11.06.1996      V3.17   Added new tooltypes IGNOREMOUSE and IGNOREDISK to
                        blanker page.

                        Added new tooltype AVOIDSUN to window page.

                        Added new tooltype DATE to patch/misc page.

                        New catalog required V3.17.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.53.

26.06.1996      V3.18   Added new tooltype FORCE_GERMAN to misc page

                        New catalog required V3.18.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.55.

01.08.1996      V3.19   Added new tooltype FORCEAMIGA to screen/patch page

                        New catalog required V3.19.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.56.

19.09.1996      V3.20   Removed some bugs with the menu shortcuts.

                        The NoCMDKey and NoESCKey were switched. Fixed.

                        Added spanish catalog.

                        New catalog required V3.20.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.57.

09.10.1996      V3.21   Removed some enforcer hits which came with
                        the template line.

                        Removed a bug with the WBGAUGE cycle gadget.

                        IF screenblank was disabled by brackets, the default
                        value was set to 360. Fixed to be 0.

                        The weight of the 'Patches' group in 'Disk' page
                        set to 0 for better looking GUI.

                        Added newest version of WBStart.library 2.2.

12.01.1997      V3.22   Added new tooltype SCREENMENU to screen/patch page.

                        New catalog required V3.22.

                        Now supporting MultiCX 2.60.

23.01.1997      V3.23   Fixed bug with closing icon.library.

                        Fixed MCX-Versionnumber routine.

                        Now supporting MCX 2.62.

                        New catalog required V3.23.

24.01.1997      V3.24   Added 'About MUI' to Project menu

                        New catalog required V 3.24.

14.02.1997      V3.25   Added new tooltype WINCENTER to window/misc page.

                        Added new tooltype WINPARENT to window/misc page.

                        Added new tooltype WINTOPLEFT to window/misc page.

                        Now supporting MCX 2.63.

                        New catalog required V 3.25.

26.03.1997      V3.26   Reworked error handling.

                        Can now be run under Workbench 2.0x 
                        (locale support available from WB2.1 and up)

25.04.1997      V3.27   Added new tooltype TITLEACTIVATE to screen/main page.

                        Added new tooltype SUNPOPUP to window/mouse page.

                        Added new tooltype WBMENU to patch/misc page.

                        Added new tooltype LEFTYMOUSE to window/mouse page.

                        Added new tooltype MAPCAPSLOCK to patch/system page.

                        Added new tooltype SCRMODEID to blanker/blanker page.

                        Added new tooltype PRTSC_LEFT to screen/main page.

                        Added new tooltype PRTSC_RIGHT to screen/main page.

                        Added new tooltype TOOLALIAS to patch/misc page.

                        Added new tooltype SUPERLAYERS to window/misc page.

                        Now supporting MCX 2.71.

                        New catalog required V 3.27.

15.05.1997      V3.28   Added new tooltype WIDE to patch/misc page.

                        New catalog required V 3.28.

31.05.1997      V3.29   Added all new DPMS tooltypes to Screen/Patch page.

                        New catalog required V 3.29.

17.06.1997      V3.30   The DPMS tooltypes got their own page on the 
                        Blanker page.

                        CLI arguments didn't work in all cases. Fixed.

                        Showwarning didn't work correctly. Fixed.

                        New catalog required V 3.30.

18.08.1997      V3.31   Added tooltype PubScreenAlias to Screen/Main page.

                        New catalog required V 3.31.

01.09.1997      V3.32   Added tooltype BLANKPRI to Blanker/Blanker page.

                        New catalog required V 3.32.

21.09.1997      V3.33   Patched version number to work with the latest
                        update of MultiCX without getting error messages
                        that You are using an older version.

21.10.1997      V3.34   Fixed routine for locale catalogs.

27.10.1997      V3.35   Added tooltype CHECK_CLOCK to Misc/Misc page.

                        New catalog required V 3.35.
